## Growing Beyond
{% if not full_stack %}

- **Adding a Vue 3 frontend:** Run `copier update --trust` and set `full_stack=true`. This restructures the project into an Nx monorepo with Vue 3 + FastAPI.
{% endif %}
{% if not enable_github_pm %}
- **Adding GitHub Project Management:** Run `copier update --trust` and set `enable_github_pm=true`. This adds issue templates, PR template, labels, and a Project board bootstrap script.
{% endif %}
- **Deploying to production:** See [`docs/productionalize.md`](docs/productionalize.md) for Docker builds, CI, health endpoints, environment management, and serving strategy.
